ZH: 农民在田地里撒肥料。
EN: The farmers spread fertilizer in the fields.

ZH: 这种肥料很适合玉米的生长。
EN: This type of fertilizer is perfect for the growth of corn.

ZH: 有机肥料对环境友好。
EN: Organic fertilizers are environmentally friendly.

ZH: 农民需要购买大量的肥料来施用。
EN: Farmers need to purchase a large amount of fertilizer for application.

ZH: 这家公司主要生产化学肥料。
EN: This company mainly produces chemical fertilizers.

ZH: 农民们在土地上撒下了新的有机肥料。
EN: Farmers spread new organic fertilizers on the land.

ZH: 蔬菜需要肥料来增加生长速度。
EN: Vegetables need fertilizer to increase their growth rate.

ZH: 他们种植大米的时候施了很多肥料。
EN: They applied a lot of fertilizer when planting rice.

ZH: 这些肥料对农作物的产量有很大益处。
EN: These fertilizers are very beneficial for crop yield.

ZH: 每年春季都要重新施肥料。
EN: Fertilizer needs to be reapplied every spring.

ZH: 水果园使用大量有机肥料来提高产量。
EN: The orchard uses a lot of organic fertilizer to increase yield.

ZH: 饲养牲畜需要的肥料也是不同的。
EN: The fertilizers needed for raising livestock are also different.

ZH: 这袋肥料可以覆盖一定面积。
EN: This bag of fertilizer can cover a certain area.

ZH: 肥料的质量直接影响作物的生长状况。
EN: The quality of fertilizers directly affects the growth of crops.

ZH: 这个农场的肥料使用率很高。
EN: The fertilizer usage rate in this farm is very high.

ZH: 农业发展需要更多绿色环保的肥料。
EN: Agricultural development requires more eco-friendly fertilizers.

ZH: 在种植水果时需要特殊种类的肥料。
EN: Special types of fertilizers are needed when planting fruits.

ZH: 这个村庄产出的肥料供应了整个地区。
EN: The fertilizer produced in this village supplies the entire region.

ZH: 动物粪便也可以作为有机肥料。
EN: Animal manure can also be used as organic fertilizer.

ZH: 这家工厂生产的化学肥料会对环境造成污染。
EN: Chemical fertilizers produced by this factory will pollute the environment.
